<hl>
<seg id=1> Gaoxin technology developing zone in Shantou city has attracted attention from both domestic and overseas merchants </seg>
</hl>
<p>
<seg id=2> Xinhua News Agency, Shantou, December 20th. Because of the improved environment and an upward tendency in investments, Gaoxin technology developing zone in Shantou city has attracted the attention of both domestic and overseas merchants. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=3> Some scientists who are natives of Chaozhou city and now live in the United States expressed their intentions of exploring the advanced technology industries inside this zone. The executive manager of Motorola in China and the concerned accountable officials of Epson company also came here to discuss the investing projects; The Taiwan merchants announced the plan of building up companies to develop technical software. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=4> Currently, inside Gaoxin technology developing zone, 180 million Yuan has been accumulated as investment capital, 370 thousand square kilometers of commercial buildings have been constructed, and the infrastructures such as water, electricity, communication, insurance, taxes, warehouses etc. are being operated in this zone. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=5> By early November of this year, 177 new projects took place in the zone with an amount of 640 million Yuan investment capital, 50% of the money came from foreign capital. Seven enterprises from this zone are regarded as the national advanced technology enterprises. </seg>
<seg id=6> This year, this zone has accumulated gross products of 370 million Yuan, 455 million Yuan income is from technologies and trades, 12,747,000 US dollar export products and 360 million Yuan tax avenues. </seg>
<seg id=7> Meanwhile, Shantou city also formulated and implemented more than ten regulations and policies in order to encourage developing technologies and new and high-tech industries with high density of knowledge. </seg>
</p>
